simuletta.compiler.SyntaxClass
simuletta.compiler.declaration.Declaration
simuletta.compiler.declaration.Profile
All Implemented Interfaces:
Externalizable, Serializable
public class Profile extends Declaration implements Externalizable
Routine Declaration. 
 Syntax:
 
                ProfileDeclaration ::= invalid input: '<' GLOBAL invalid input: '<' ( identifying'StringValue ) >? >?
                          PROFILE profile'identifier  ParameterSpecification  END
 
                        ParameterSpecification ::= invalid input: '<' IMPORT invalid input: '<' Type localid invalid input: '<' , localid >* >+ >?  invalid input: '<' EXPORT Type Identifier >?
                                                 | invalid input: '<' IMPORT invalid input: '<' Type localid invalid input: '<' , localid >* >+ >?  invalid input: '<' EXIT LABEL Identifier >?
 
 S-Code:
 
 
                RoutineProfile ::= PROFILE profile:newtag
                                                        invalid input: '<' ImportDefinition >* invalid input: '<' Export  |  Exit >?
                                                   ENDPROFILE

                Peculiar ::= KNOWN body:newtag kid:string
                                  |  SYSTEM body:newtag sid:string
                                  |  EXTERNAL body:newtag nature:string xid:string
                                  |  INTERFACE pid:string
  
                ImportDefinition ::= IMPORT parm:newtag QuantityDescriptor
  
                Export ::= EXPORT parm:newtag ResolvedType
                Exit   ::= EXIT return:newtag
